<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">Гурба Владимир Николаевич, доктор социологических наук, заместитель Полномочного Представителя Президента РФ в Южном федеральном округе</span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">Главный редактор</span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">Фокин Николай Игоревич, </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: mceinline; font-size: small; color: #000000;">кандидат педагогических наук, доцент</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><strong style="font-size: x-small; color: #000000; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"> Ответственный секретарь</span></span></span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"> Сухорукова Людмила Михайловна, </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: mceinline; font-size: small; color: #000000;"> доктор педагогических наук, профессор.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 18.0pt 45.0pt;" align="center"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"> Вопросы для рассмотрения в публикациях:</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 115%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; background: white;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"> «Образование. Наука. Инновации: южное измерение» - международный, междисциплинарный рецензируемый журнал открытого доступа, публикующий оригинальные научные статьи c результатами передовых теоретических и прикладных исследований по актуальным проблемам теории и практики образования. </span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 115%;"><span style="background-color: white; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">Среди рассматриваемых на страницах «Образование. Наука. Инновации: южное измерение» тем: </span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="text" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white;"><span style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Теория и история педагогики</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="text" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white;"><span style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Теория и практика педагогического образования</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="text" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Теоретический и прикладные исследования  непрерывного образования</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Менеджмент и экономика образования</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Мигрантская (миграционная) педагогика, миграционный менеджмент в образовании</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Безопасность образования</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Кадетское и военное образование</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- <span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Проблемы глобального и регионального управления образованием и </span>деятельность международных институтов развития образования, в том числе в странах южного измерения - глобальной оси «Юг - Юг»</span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Науковедение</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Инновационная практика</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- <span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Рецензии и обзоры</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;"><span style="font-family: mceinline;">- Темы, заявленные автором. </span></span></span></span></span></p>
